text: Natalia Vladimirovna Poklonskaya (; ; born 18 March 1980) is a Russian politician. She is a Deputy of the State Duma of Russia, deputy chairman of the State Duma Committee on Foreign Affairs since 18 September 2016. ==Notes== ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Members of the State Duma Category:Russian military people Category:Russian lawyers Category:Ukrainian military people Category:Politicians from Luhansk Oblast
